data.description: Adorable Country Walk 4/2 home with a spacious open/split floor plan. The fully fenced yard borders a conservation area for additional privacy. The details and personal touches throughout make this house a home. Don't let the square footage keep you from taking a look! Great floorplan and additional space not included in heated and cooled square footage but could be 5th bedroom, playroom or home office!   In addition to the 4 bedrooms, the garage has been converted to additional bedroom space but can easily be returned to the intended use. If you have a buyer who would be interested in a short-term lease back that would be ideal!
